<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Oct1931"><font color="red">27 October 1931</font> <i>Letters III and BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I finished pulling together the first 8 episodes last night and as I am quite fatigued and it a splendid day Giorgio is taking us for a long country drive &hellip; To my great relief I find that much more of the book is done than I had hoped for </div>
